hmn / haltmission             Halts (resets) the current mission

   Format:
      ;hmn                    Halts the current mission

   Notes:
      Once a mission is halted, it can only be restarted from the very
         beginning.
      See the help for ';startmission' for more information about missions.

   User commands:
      hmn / haltmn / haltmission
